items.title: Denver Broncos' Alex Singelton opens up on cancer diagnosis: 'Thought about it 24/7'
items.description: Denver Bronces linebacker Alex Singelton is opening up to "Good Morning America" on his testicular cancer diagnosis.

items.title: 5 dead, including 3 children, in Colorado car crash, police say
